#carousel
  .row
    .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
      script.
        $(document).ready(function ()
        {
          $('#carousel .bxslider').bxSlider({
          pager:          true,
          touchEnabled:   false,
          adaptiveHeight: true,
          onSlideBefore:  function ()
          {
          if (window.top.scrollY != 0)
          {
          window.scrollTo(0, 0);
            }
            }
          });
        });
      ul.bxslider
        li#who-wants-pink
          .row
            .col-md-6.col-md-push-6
              img.img-responsive.pull-right(src='../images/illustration-hands-cloud.png',
              alt='Illustration Hands Cloud')
            .col-md-6.col-md-pull-6
              h1.text-pink Who wants some pink?
              p
                | ASK- Fast is a cloud communication solution that
                | is designed and developed for developers and businesses.
              p
                | You can simply develop an automated communication
                | for your application or your customer service.
              p
                a.btn.btn-primary(href='#') Join Now
        li#writing-a-letter
          .row
            .col-md-6.col-md-push-6
              img.img-responsive.pull-right(src='../images/stock-man-business.png',
              alt='Picture of business man with typewriter')
            .col-md-6.col-md-pull-6
              h1.text-pink Writing a letter to your customer?
              p
                | How great is that. If you do not want to focus on efficiency fine.
                | ASK-Fast would like to provide better tools to you for your business.
                | Power of full customisation is waiting for you and many opportunities too…
              p
                a.btn.btn-primary(href='#') Join Now
        li#use-your-fingers
          .row
            .col-md-6.col-md-push-6
              img.img-responsive.pull-right(src='../images/stock-fingers.png',
              alt='Picture of fingers')
            .col-md-6.col-md-pull-6
              h1.text-pink Use your fingers for a better communication.
              p
                | We do, we are coders. We are providing you a full-fetched API for SMS,
                | E-mail, Automated Phone call, Twitter at the same time. We are keeping
                | all the hard work for ourselves and want you to use your fingers for a
                | better communication experience.
              p
                a.btn.btn-primary(href='#') Join Now


